original_title: Chikara: More Songs About Buildings & Food
overview: Claudio Castagnoli has a "European Rules" contest in a featured bout. Lance Steel arrives in 2004 to make his CHIKARA debut, and makes history by picking a fight with the ornery Darkness Crabtree! In a once-in-a-lifetime relevos atomicos match, Jigsaw, Jolly Roger, Shane Storm & DJ Skittlez fight Larry Sweeney, ShareCropper, Crossbones & American Gigolo!
title: Chikara: More Songs About Buildings & Food
